- Arduino Uno R3;
- RaspberryPi B+ with a modified version of Raspbian with jasper already installed;
- Infineon MotorShield for Arduino;
- ultrasound sensor HC-SR04;
- Stepper motors (Nema17) with drivers (EasyDriver 4.4);
- 2x Usb batteries for stepper motor and raspberry pi ;
- 2x 9V batteries ( for arduino and brush motor);
- An old Rc car re-adapted for carry all these things.

